headline: Dave & Buster's, Genesco, Leggett & Platt, Matthews, and Mohawk Industries Shares Plummet, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks fell in the afternoon session after a significant downward revision of U.S. job creation data raised concerns about the health of the economy.
